We should stick to the api design of the already available `/vulndb` endpoints.

We would like to have a database frontend for the malicious package database and open-source insights. 

There will be two pages:
- A listing page, listing the search results of the query (including a search for packages)
- A details page of a specific package


Currently devguard does not provide any API-Endpoints to implement this functionality. Thus we need to first mock the data when doing the API-Request. 

